<div class="forum-post-quote"><p class="forum-post-quoted-name">Maureen I</p><p style="margin-top:0;">Dear Gerritt</p><p>..I may still feel a sensation or emotion arising but my attention doesn't feel so drawn to go there... It's so hard to describe but the looking really is foolproof, it's just 'me' I'm looking at and i'm always here..the same as the 'you' you are looking at..</p><p>much love , thanks for all you share.</p><p>Maureen</p></div><p>Great post Maureen, this has been my experience as well. Old habits, thinking, ways of being that didn't really serve me just fell to the wayside. You are correct, the Looking is foolproof, and this is good news... <img src="smilies/smile.png" alt="smily"></p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
