<div class="forum-post-quote"><p class="forum-post-quoted-name">gerrit</p><p style="margin-top:0;">How nice it would be if I could one day have that barrier removed and open my heart up to the world. Gerrit</p></div><p>Dear Gerrit,</p><p>... I think maybe you just did.</p><p>With love,</p><p>Dawn</p>
